<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="box_text">

<p>Linkpager is based on the idea of storing your internet favorites and granting the ability to share them with others. By visiting the Linkpager website, you are accepting the following conditions of this privacy policy.</p> 

<h2>Information Collected by Linkpager</h2>
<p>Linkpager only collects personal information relevant to the purpose of the website. Registration to use the services provided by this site may include select personal information such as name, city, state, and e-mail address.</p>
<h2>Information Security</h2>
<p>Your Linkpager account information is password protected for your security and privacy. You can protect against unauthorized use of your account by logging off once you have finished using the site.</p>
<h2>Users Under 18 Years of Age</h2>
<p>An individual must be 13 years of age or older to register to use the Linkpager website. We recommend that minors between the ages of 13 and 18 receive their parents' permission before sending information about themselves or anyone else over the Internet.</p>
