<p>If you decide to visit the Linkpager website, your visit and any possible dispute over privacy is subject to this <a href="Privacy.aspx" title="Privacy Policy">Privacy Policy</a> and our <a href="Terms.aspx" title="Terms of Use">Terms of Use</a>, including limitations on damages, arbitration of disputes, and application of Indiana state law.</p>
<h2>Effective Date of this Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>This Privacy Policy is effective as of January 1, 2011.</p>

